Antarkan helikopter Soviet itu.

325
00:29:12,173 --> 00:29:14,342
Sampai saat itu...

326
00:29:16,260 --> 00:29:18,429
Bantu kami membunuh orang jahat.

327
00:29:49,168 --> 00:29:51,003
Komandan.

328
00:29:57,343 --> 00:29:59,762
Tn. Becker. Mengikuti?

